<p>The image of the <b>evil clown</b> is a development in <a href="/wiki/United_States" title="United States">American</a> <a href="/wiki/Popular_culture" title="Popular culture">popular culture</a>, in which the playful <a href="/wiki/Trope_(literature)" title="Trope (literature)">trope</a> of the <a href="/wiki/Clown" title="Clown">clown</a> is rendered as disturbing through the use of <a href="/wiki/Horror_and_terror" title="Horror and terror">horror</a> elements and <a href="/wiki/Dark_humor" title="Dark humor" class="mw-redirect">dark humor</a>.</p>
